{"recipe_desc": "Making your own ricotta cheese at home is fairly easy and well worth the added effort to make better food. Note: Even if it's organic, do not use ultra-pasteurized milk for this recipe as it will not curdle properly.", "recipe_category": ["Homemade Ingredients"], "recipe_image": ["/recipes/homemade-ricotta-cheese/homemade-ricotta-cheese.jpg"], "recipe_total_time": ["PT1H"], "recipe_published_time": ["Sep 26, 2012"], "image_urls": ["http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/homemade-ricotta-cheese/homemade-ricotta-cheese.jpg"], "recipe_ingredients": ["\u00bd gallon high-quality whole milk", "\u00bd teaspoon salt", "3 tablespoons lemon juice (from 3 lemons)", "additional lemon juice (if needed)", "cheesecloth"], "recipe_prep_time": ["PT10M"], "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<title>Homemade Ricotta Cheese Recipe - MakeBetterFood.com</title>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;charset=utf-8\" />\n<link href=\"http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Brawler\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<link href=\"/css/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" />\n<!--[if lte IE 7]>\n<link href=\"/css/ie7.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\"/>\n<![endif]-->\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" />\n<link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"MakeBetterFood.com - Recipes, Learn How to Cook Amazing Food\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/MakeBetterFood\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Homemade Ricotta Cheese Recipe\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"food\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/homemade-ricotta-cheese/\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"http://www.makebetterfood.com/recipes/homemade-ricotta-cheese/homemade-ricotta-cheese.jpg\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"MakeBetterFood.com\"/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Making your own ricotta cheese at h